HEADWORD: Halacha
<hw>Ha*la"cha</hw> <pr>(h⟦adot⟧*l⟦aum⟧"k⟦adot⟧)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>;
<plu><it>pl.</it> <plw>Halachoth</plw> <pr>(-k⟦omac⟧th)</pr>.</plu>
<ety>[Heb. <ets>hal⟦amac⟧ch⟦amac⟧h</ets>.]</ety> <def>The general term
